#CHIP YM2203
#CLOCK 3579545

; YM2203 (OPN) SSG (Square/Sawtooth/Noise) Channels Test
;
; The YM2203 has 3 SSG channels that operate independently of the FM engine.
; These channels support square waves, envelope control, and noise.
;
; Tests SSG channels:
; - Envelope variations
; - Tone/Noise mixing
; - Register accuracy

#TRACK 0

TEMPO 120

; SSG Channel 1: Square wave melody
c4 . d4 . e4 .

r4

; SSG Channel 2: With envelope
f4 . . g4 . .

r4

; SSG Channel 3: Noise channel
r4 . . .

r4

; Mixed tone/noise
c4 . n . d4 . n .

r4

r2

#END
